  no install method.
- `hilavitkutin-api::WorkUnitBundle` and
  `hilavitkutin-api::StoreBundle` for the api primitives the
  Kit's associated types target. The engine reads them at compile
  time on `.add_kit::<K>()`; providers never imports the engine.
- `hilavitkutin-str::{Str, StringInterner, ArenaInterner}` for the
  interner contract this crate's `MemoryArena` implements.
- `hilavitkutin-api::HasMemoryProvider` / `MemoryProviderApi` for
  the provider-pattern this crate's `HasInterner` / `InternerApi`
  parallels.
